00:05:22.097 --> 00:05:24.715
by this f of x function.

00:05:24.715 --> 00:05:27.247
But these are the exact same rectangles.

00:05:27.247 --> 00:05:28.848
And they have the exact same heights.

00:05:28.848 --> 00:05:31.265
And the limit as you get
more and more of these

00:05:31.265 --> 00:05:32.264
by making them thinner and thinner,

00:05:32.264 --> 00:05:33.480
is gonna be the same
as the limit as you get

00:05:33.480 --> 00:05:35.630
more and more of these as
